{"tid":1388200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中85討論] 香港人已經 沒有退路 只可以贏","createTime":"2019-07-30T16:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T22:41:16.000Z","uid":100372,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84854c582f3d7a318e463502e1cef8827e11a198","tid":1388200,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:07:46.000Z","msg":"元朗打人 真係暴動個班人唔去清算<br />\n清算班手無寸鐵嘅後生仔<br />\n呢個政府我已經冇抱任何希望<br />\n<br />\n點解重有班天真嬌係到ff陪審團？<br />\n點解唔反思一下 <br />\n佢地根本係連控告我地都唔應該 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">憑咩入班後生暴動罪<br />\n我地邊忽暴動？</span><br />\n重點係陪審團係抽出黎<br />\n咪係到ff咁多 以為實抽到自己人<br />\n唔比抽到深藍 <br />\n大家唔細啦 唔好咁天真<br />\n都有天琦同g鋒做前車之鑑<br />\n呢個政府搵籍口拉政治犯唔係第一日啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人 只可以贏呢一役</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">唯有贏左 先可以醫好香港<br />\n唯有贏左 先可以有真普選 </span></strong></span><br />\n咩元朗鄉黑 黑警 港共政府 <br />\n每日150 大灣區  明日大嶼<br />\n真係數唔撚到有幾多問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該主力推 8月5號嘅全民大罷工post<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>全部人同我每日番工放工air drop<br />\n人多食飯air drop<br />\n係啲人多嘅group到air drop<br />\n做好文宣工作<br />\n好好討論8月5號嘅打機攻略 </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n個啲助養飯劵啊 請小朋友食飯啊<br />\n比正皮 like post前同我用腦諗一諗<br />\n個堆全部p牌仔出post<br />\n同堆諗多兩秒都知實行極難同費時<br />\n又會比位啲狗同狗公入<br />\n咁大個人 唔好見正皮多 <br />\n又係熱門就like左先啦<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">比人帶緊風向啦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">集中討論 8月5 <br />\n香城主線任務<br />\n香城人嘅打機攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n依加事態發展已經唔係單純反送中 <br />\n<strong>係一場救港嘅光復運動</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n沒有退路 只可以贏 </span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4D1FFUc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4D1FFUc.png&h=a319f115&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20d9008626091fd124a554fceb9b95d670fe634c","tid":1388200,"uid":100372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"理性討論 <br />\n七區會唔會分散左隊友<br />\n打機好似唔係咁打"},{"pid":"53bb4ebfe094cd37cbed89d95b492825a58d219c","tid":1388200,"uid":100372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:09:26.000Z","msg":"會唔會集中係同一區打怪易打贏啲？<br />\n戰線太多 好咩？"},{"pid":"ecc8c6bce1e621d69eb0e7946b593ae912b24719","tid":1388200,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:09:46.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選應要排最頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私咁，過埋2047都死左啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"e356e16fe02b5c3d441d03c3b211e388a4d5de89","tid":1388200,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:10:07.000Z","msg":"push 推上熱門警世"},{"pid":"a4f4bd3c164796306d9fc235c7728a3bc2fdc354","tid":1388200,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:10:34.000Z","msg":"pushhhhh"},{"pid":"b349857984f3621f0fc93cb688a31e1b6dddce91","tid":1388200,"uid":132189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:10:50.000Z","msg":"有機會拎到槍都冇人敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55ee5d48254d708cdebf248181f74e78d4a005f","tid":1388200,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:12:42.000Z","msg":"對家又講到出水炮車又成 <br />\n隊友分到咁散 好難打怪 <br />\nfirst aid法師都唔知要去邊區補血"},{"pid":"51a6066b70a73fc24115ce13ddb1bf1a63463d65","tid":1388200,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:13:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8c591ce6f8b3f38979eeabeaa1cc4b9831b52293","tid":1388200,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8月5全民大罷工"},{"pid":"f9632d8acc88d1723f14d1402fcdad57f5a28828","tid":1388200,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"Pushhhh"},{"pid":"41f983c5b4c5b7e277e49ff3b06589174ccc9ff8","tid":1388200,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>幫手推post唔該</strong></span>"},{"pid":"870e6c23e2f34691aff0db042676e4827540c33f","tid":1388200,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41f983c5b4c5b7e277e49ff3b06589174c